{"tid":104612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關南亞人歧視問題（UST南亞仔請入）","createTime":"2017-02-02T08:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:35:09.000Z","uid":24547,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3d74767856f03740c4ccf980d0260439be8624","tid":104612,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"首先南亞人係香港過百年，一直都相安無事。<br />\n只不過係近年D假難民係香港犯案搞臭你地個朵，你地D PR唔係應該放番係治安日常方面咩？<br />\n好心你地唔好咁on9成意為黃種人歧視你地文化宗教，成日宣傳&quot;我地係南亞人，This is what we are，要尊重我地bla bla bla&quot;，其實未重黑人憎同令人覺得&quot;我地係南亞人，(打刧強姦斬人)This is what we are，要尊重我地bla bla bla&quot;。與其嘥咁多錢係D文化PR度，點解你地唔夜晚出街捉D假難民，做黑警，做保安etc。<br />\n坦白講你地D文化關我地黃種人閪事，拜阿拉或濕婆無人想理，香港人咁膚淺，你一講英文無人會理你係邊到來。最緊要係唔好比到人有&quot;夜晚就會有一堆面目模糊嘅南亞人就會出街打刧強姦斬人&quot;嘅印象就冇人會想理你地。"},{"pid":"a413de75167e3fa2f81a5188e5883ec8ad042980","tid":104612,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"條友去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c13cf9ae138fbe89c8d501c033231fb9d366e1e","tid":104612,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"啱呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244ebfeb01777edc20ab5c330cb237723c695910","tid":104612,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"我絕對支持反假難民 不過形象呢家野破壞容易 建立難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278fbad4606658bd06d6d8a9c510d0d143b05418","tid":104612,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我絕對支持反假難民 不過形象呢家野破壞容易 建立難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔行動？自組夜晚巡邏隊有幾難?"},{"pid":"6bf43fa896fec0c6fc2011e42eeaa702d517e39c","tid":104612,"uid":